twitter.title: Sen. Paul, Scott Brown hold GOP unity rally: Some protest outside Huddleston Hall event
twitter.description: DURHAM — Fresh off his win in the New Hampshire Republican primary, Scott Brown stopped by Huddleston Hall at the University of New Hampshire on Friday afternoon with Kentucky Sen. Rand Paul to hold a unity rally.University of New Hampshire Student Body President Joseph Sweeney. also a state representative, kicked off the rally with a passionate speech dedicated to Brown.“Scott will be an independent voice for our state, fighting for students and their families,” Sweeney said.
